{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DdJGNC4V6n7TSSAw7z2c3N","type":"tool_result","content":"   436→- [ ] [backend] DB client module (`src/db.ts`): connection pool (`pg` or `postgres` library), typed query functions for: `insertRound`, `updateRoundPhase`, `getRoundByPda`, `getRoundsByPhase`, `insertOperatorEvent`. Phase transitions must be unidirectional (application-level guard). `updated_at` set on every phase change. `secret` column never logged.\n   437→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"06cad3ba-f7e8-434b-bb69-4c100d6ca881","uuid":"a7deb8d7-e959-4aa1-8b9d-9f8eb8d05c85","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/006-fairness-backend/spec.md","content":"- [ ] [backend] DB client module (`src/db.ts`): connection pool (`pg` or `postgres` library), typed query functions for: `insertRound`, `updateRoundPhase`, `getRoundByPda`, `getRoundsByPhase`, `insertOperatorEvent`. Phase transitions must be unidirectional (application-level guard). `updated_at` set on every phase change. `secret` column never logged.\n","numLines":2,"startLine":436,"totalLines":524}}}
